        <p id="P_146">
                <b id="B_147">Step 5:</b> To begin the sparge process, convert your bottling bucket into a lauter tun. How to build a lauter tun:<br id="BR_148" /> a) Insert Phil’s False Bottom attached to stopper and hose<br id="BR_149" /> b) Fit stopper to hole in bottling bucket<br id="BR_150" /> c) Clamp off hose
              </p>
